    <item>
      <title>Migration brief</title>
      <link>https://jxx.joshix.com/2016/06/12/migration-brief/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jun 2016 04:18:56 -0800</pubDate>
      <author>j@joshix.com (Josh Wood)</author>
      <guid>https://jxx.joshix.com/2016/06/12/migration-brief/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/joshix/jxnu&#34;&gt;jxnu&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo; project put the site&amp;rsquo;s old content atop new infrastructure. This is a mostly-migrated version of the once and future joshix.com:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Built with &lt;a href=&#34;http://gohugo.io&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hugo&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;served by the &lt;a href=&#34;https://caddyserver.com&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Caddy&lt;/em&gt; web server&lt;/a&gt; with automatic
&lt;em&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s Encrypt&lt;/em&gt; TLS and HTTP/2,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;packaged in a discrete &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/appc/spec&#34;&gt;App Container Image (ACI)&lt;/a&gt; based on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/joshix/caddybox&#34;&gt;caddybox&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;executed by the &lt;a href=&#34;https://coreos.com/rkt/&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;rkt&lt;/code&gt; container engine&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;running on &lt;a href=&#34;https://coreos.com/os/docs/latest/&#34;&gt;CoreOS Linux&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
